TY  - JOUR
TI  - Changes in body composition and muscle function after radical cystectomy
JO  - BJU Int
PY  - 2008
VL  - 101
SP  - 973
AU  - Mathur S
AB  - We measured changes in body composition muscle function and energy expenditure after radical cystectomy. Eleven consecutive men underwent measurements before surgery and at two and six months. Total body protein and resting energy expenditure were assessed using validated methods in this prospective observational study of nutritional decline.
