TI  - The MoveTrial: prehabilitation in muscle invasive bladder cancer study protocol
JO  - J Urol
PY  - 2024
VL  - 211
SP  - e60
AU  - Zed A
AU  - Yad B
AB  - Prehabilitation programs aim to improve functional capacity before treatment in muscle invasive bladder cancer. We describe the protocol of a randomized controlled trial evaluating a home based exercise intervention. Feasibility usability and preliminary efficacy are the main outcomes of this ongoing multicenter study of prehabilitation.
